---
title: Teriyaki Prawn & Ginger Veggie Stir-Fry with Rapid Rice & Lime
description: Say hello to bold flavours and speedy cooking with this stir-fry spectacular! Juicy prawns, crisp veggies, and fragrant ginger sizzle in a glossy teriyaki glaze, all served over fluffy rice. It’s fresh, fast, and packed with deliciousness!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/67ca4c2125f33d23e0b3dbc3-f5104664.jpeg
